  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: no-referrer-when-downgrade

  # ‚ö†Ô∏è IMPORTANTE:
  # Netlify **no permite** Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy, COOP, CORP.
